### Example 06 — event hooks

### Provider health
GET http://localhost:4455/odata/v4/logistics/Shipments?$top=2

### Local target (likely empty on first request)
GET http://localhost:4106/odata/v4/example/Shipments?$top=2

### Per-batch metrics captured by the WRITE_BATCH hook
GET http://localhost:4106/odata/v4/example/BatchMetrics?$orderby=writtenAt desc&$top=5

### Pipeline registered
GET http://localhost:4106/pipeline/Pipelines?$filter=name eq 'Shipments'
